        WEB_SITE=http://github.com/troydm/easytree.vim/
         ENTERED=20160430
         UPDATED=20160430
           SHORT="A simple tree file manager for vim"

cat << EOF
easytree.vim - is a simple tree file manager for vim. It's approach to a file
management and takes a more traditional vim yank/paste file copy/paste/delete
approach It's also more simpler in it's functionality and has much less features
compared to other file managers.
It's goal is to be as fast and as minimalistic as possible.
Just the right tool for just the right task 
EOF
